'''Nérée Boubée''' (1806 in [[Toulouse]] &ndash; 1862 in [[Bagnères-de-Luchon|Luchon]]) was a [[naturalist]], [[entomologist]], [[geologist]], author and a professor at the [[University of Paris]]. He was a Member of the [[Société entomologique de France]].

In 1845 he established a [[natural history]] dealership and publishing house, the still very successful Maison d'édition Boubée.

