{{Infobox telescope|style=proposed [[optical telescope]]}}
The '''Space Solar Telescope''' (SST) is a planned Chinese [[optical telescope|optical]] [[space telescope|space]] [[solar telescope]]. It was first proposed in the 1990s, and is intended to be a {{convert|1|m|ft}} telescope.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.spacedaily.com/reports/China_Exclusive_Scientists_looking_for_site_for_giant_solar_telescope_999.html |title=China Exclusive: Scientists looking for site for giant solar telescope |author=Xinhua |author-link=Xinhua|date=2012-08-29|accessdate= 2012-09-06|work=Space Daily}}</ref>

